PrecisRegulations Amending the FIREARMS FEES REGULATIONS by repealing section 21.1 whereby a credit of $35 was established for those who paid the full price for a "possession-only" firearms licence prior to June 10, 2000, which could then be used to offset the cost of renewing that Licence or for the issuance or renewal of a Possession & Acquisition Licence.
